id we are updating.  For that, I write a custom validation method.  This method is in the table controller:  public void ValidateOwner(string id)
{
    var result = Lookup(id).Queryable.PerUserFilter(UserId).FirstOrDefault TodoItem ();
    if (result == null)
    {
        throw new HttpResponseException(HttpStatusCode.NotFound);
    }
