This view is much simpler than the Angular view because none of the markup for the actual application is contained within the view.  All markup is done by the React components in our code.  There are three files referenced in this file that do not yet exist.  The JavaScript files will be created by the Webpack bundler, and the 
app.css
 file is the 
regular CSS file
 from the normal Quickstart application.


